OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes spoke to Chris Kamara
OL,8,Fat an event in Manchester
OL,10,FFormer footballer has been recalling
OL,11,Fhow he "suffered in silence" for
OL,12,Falmost two years before he was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with a speech disorder.
OL,15,FThe 66-year-old was told he has
OL,16,Fapraxia of speech - a neurological
OL,17,Fcondition which affects the brain
OL,18,Fpathways involved in planning the
OL,19,Fmovements needed to speak.
