OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,FKamara, who is affectionately known as
OL,7,F"Kammy" and renowned for his famous
OL,8,Fcatchphrase "Unbelievable Jeff!", in
OL,9,F2022 after fans noticed he was
OL,10,Fslurring his words.
OL,12,FChris has been raising awareness at an
OL,13,Fevent in Manchester and speaking about
OL,14,Fhow the condition has affected him.
OL,16,F"You think exactly the same, but then
OL,17,Fthe passage from the brain to the
OL,18,Fmouth is either non-existent or
OL,19,Fintermittent." he said.
