OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F"I would know exactly what I was
OL,7,Fsaying, but the words wouldn't come
OL,8,Fout.
OL,10,F"It was terrifying at the time. People
OL,11,Factually thought I was drunk or had
OL,12,Fhad a stroke when I was doing my
OL,13,Fbroadcasts."
OL,15,FChris is now supporting the campaign
OL,16,Fgroup which aims to make speech and
OL,17,Flanguage therapy available to all
OL,18,Fchildren.
OL,20,FHe said: "This is our first official
OL,21,FSpeech and Language Conference.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
