OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F"We're aiming to get speech and
OL,7,Flanguage therapy for all children, and
OL,8,Fthen we'll work on the adults after
OL,9,Fthat, but the children need it first.
OL,11,F"It's important that we raise
OL,12,Fawareness.
OL,14,F"It took me almost two years to accept
OL,15,Fmy condition and now it's my duty to
OL,16,Fhelp others
OL,18,F"The biggest plus that's come out of
OL,19,Fall this, is that I do have that
OL,20,Fplatform to help other people."
