OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,FMikey's Wish was started by a then 13-
OL,7,Fyear-old Mikey Akers, who himself has
OL,8,Fapraxia.
OL,10,FAfter being diagnosed at two-years-
OL,11,Fold, he had 13 years of Speech and
OL,12,FLanguage Therapy (SLT), just to be
OL,13,Fable to communicate with others.
OL,15,FNow 23, he says he set up Mikey's Wish
OL,16,Fso other sufferers don't feel the
OL,17,Fisolation that he did.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
