OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F"There was just nothing out there so I
OL,7,Fdecided to start Mikey's Wish to help
OL,8,Fother families and children who are
OL,9,Fgoing through their journey to not
OL,10,Ffeel the loneliness that I felt and
OL,11,Fthat my mum felt," he said
OL,13,FGeorgia Wilson from Sale in Greater
OL,14,FManchester agrees that more needs to
OL,15,Fbe done to help children with speech
OL,16,Fproblems.
OL,18,FHer six-year old Zach has had speech
OL,19,Fand language therapy to treat his
OL,20,Fapraxia, and it's made a big
OL,21,Fdifference to his speech.
