OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,FBut it's come at a cost, his parents
OL,7,Fhave had to find #10,000 for his
OL,8,Fprivate treatment.
OL,10,FShe said: "It was really difficult to
OL,11,Faccess help, but also needing a
OL,12,Ftherapist with the right expertise for
OL,13,Fchildhood apraxia of speech.
OL,15,F"It was really important that Zach was
OL,16,Freceiving the speech therapy so we
OL,17,Factually funded a lot of it ourselves.
