OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F"We've done it as a family, one week
OL,7,Fhis grandma pays, the next week maybe
OL,8,Fmy mum pays, and me and my husband the
OL,9,Fweek after, and that's how we've done
OL,10,Fit for the last couple of years.
OL,12,F"It's cost us around ten thousand
OL,13,Fpounds. The funding just isn't there."
OL,15,FSteve Jamieson, CEO of the , says
OL,16,Fthere is a "massive problem'' due to a
OL,17,Fshortage of speech and language
OL,18,Ftherapists".
