OL,3,CChris Kamara: 'It's my duty to help
OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F"We have children waiting up to 52
OL,7,Fweeks for an initial assessment, often
OL,8,Fthat initial assessment takes place
OL,9,Fthen the child goes on to a separate
OL,10,Fwaiting list to then get treatment or
OL,11,Ftherapy, so it may be even longer
OL,12,Fbefore that therapy starts.
OL,14,F"The impact on these children is
OL,15,Fmassive. It has a major effect on
OL,16,Ftheir schooling, their basic
OL,17,Fcommunication skills and a huge impact
OL,18,Fon their families and their lives.
