OL,4,Cothers with speech problems'
OL,6,F" Their communication ability is so
OL,7,Ffar behind other children at a similar
OL,8,Fage."
OL,10,F"What we are calling for is to train
OL,11,Fmore speech and language therapists.
OL,12,FWe need to get more people into the
OL,13,Fprofession." he said.
